FBIS4-15451 "drsov068_v_94015" FBIS-SOV-94-068 Daily Report 7 Apr 1994 Lithuania Homeland Union Head Criticizes Indexation Decision Homeland Union Head Criticizes Indexation Decision WS0704163494 Vilnius ELTA in English 1300 GMT 7 Apr 94 WS0704163494 Vilnius ELTA English BFN [From "News Bulletin" No. 472] [Text] Vilnius, April 6, ELTA -- Chairman of Homeland Union Board Gediminas Vagnorius criticized the decision of Government on indexation of enterprise property at a news conference on Wednesday [6 April]. Vagnorius claimed that the decision did not provide the restoration of the value of the artificially devalued state property and of the earlier issued shares.
